00031 extern const char* _parseName(const char* rawName);
00032 template<typename T>
00033 const char* GetClassName() {
00034   // g++ guaranteed threadsafe of local static initialization
00035   static const char* name = _parseName(__PRETTY_FUNCTION__);
00036   return name;
00037 }
